# Brainstorms

This directory holds pre-plan brainstorm artifacts emitted by **Phase 0.5** of
`skills/start/_planning.md` (the pressure-test step between `flywheel_discover`
and `flywheel_plan`).

Each file is named `<goal-slug>-<YYYY-MM-DD>.md` and captures:

- The synthesized framing of the goal after the three-question dialogue
- User answers to the pressure-test questions (smallest / 10x / adjacent)
- Any free-form "Other" text supplied via `AskUserQuestion`

The `flywheel_plan` tool reads the most-recent brainstorm (matching the current
goal slug) and feeds its synthesized framing into the planner agent prompts so
that Phase 0.5 findings shape the plan rather than being discarded.

Do not hand-edit files written by Phase 0.5. Re-run the dialogue (e.g. via
"Start over") to regenerate.
